# Anthropic API key for the Messages API (same key as ANTHROPIC_API_KEY on Anthropic’s console).
# Create at https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys — value must start with sk-ant-api03- (or sk-ant-api04-).
# This is not a Cursor/Claude Code subscription key; those will produce 401 invalid x-api-key.
CLAUDE_API_KEY=

# Optional. Full Messages URL; base host is derived for the SDK (default: https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages).
# CLAUDE_API_URL=https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages
